meta.title: What did I learn this week (2021) - 52

pageProps.content:
• https://www.pullrequest.com/ provides code review as a service.

  • How to draw an S curve in web.
  • Finnish babies are sleeping in cardboard boxes.
  • Found a free ebook - The Scientist and Engineer's Guide to Digital Signal Processing.
